,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=07de13da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=883dd080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"458712aa5eba0aa969b43fe831d7227d30582d76","tid":1816744,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14811a6af0fae19142986650333ac005e5592bf9","tid":1816744,"uid":290766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d585428d40e31d0f67eff89ed103c3d9423a03a","tid":1816744,"uid":185435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"蘚戒奶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:21:53.000Z","msg":"係邊區？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"個意思唔係生廯要戒奶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac43cf7b7f91d0e5f4bcd594af49bc5a9aa263f4","tid":1816744,"uid":341158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e9863d693eb98895f1cce0cafdc4553a57a4a4","tid":1816744,"uid":290766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"想要皮膚專科醫生推介，最好係有料到同細心<br />\n謝謝<br />\nMany many thanks!!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"陳厚毅"},{"pid":"66d327929af0a11837b7b41e7e271dcb1612f5b6"